comments: Caldwell-Pope (LAL) and Collins (ATL) briefly engage and disengage after the screen.
Huerter (ATL) makes marginal contact to Davis' (LAL) side on his driving shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) makes incidental contact with Reddish's (ATL) head.
Collins (ATL) moves into Davis's (LAL) body and initiates contact that affects his SQBR.
Capela (ATL) sets the screen on Schroder (LAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Schroder (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position on Young (ATL) during the drive .
James (LAL) makes contact with the ball during Capela's (ATL) shot attempt.
James (LAL) receives the ball in the air and takes three steps prior to the release of his shot.
Reddish (ATL) makes marginal contact with James (LAL) during his shot attempt.
Schroder (LAL) cleanly steals the ball from Young (ATL).
Collins (ATL) maintains a legal guarding position on James (LAL).
Huerter (ATL) commits a take foul on James (LAL).
Young (ATL) makes marginal contact with Davis (LAL) before the shot attempt.
Davis (LAL) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Young (ATL).
Young (ATL) commits a take foul on James (LAL).
